{"data":{"page":{"id":"3370e69d-ae91-51a8-922a-75ea7efe8b00","html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d30badcc882143b80a891a6693bfd178/89cd4/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 960px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d30badcc882143b80a891a6693bfd178/89cd4/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d30badcc882143b80a891a6693bfd178/80bba/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/d30badcc882143b80a891a6693bfd178/89cd4/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Bonsai is a hierarchy management tool to search, view and adjust employee data coming from Active Directory.</p>\n<p>I owned the 100% of the front-end work in this project. Initially, I designed a clickable prototype with Adobe XD to test the user journeys with my team. Then I built a prototype with the usual React boilerplate and a custom design. Later on, the app received more features and eventually, a new design that I also implemented.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/86f71fe6cc7492bd8695c846509f4926/877ff/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"positio